snippet.title: KCCh 20twel....13:  Some abilities and such
snippet.description:
"It's Kirby's 20th anniversary.  We've got to at least get a video uploaded by the end of the year."

Aaand we barely... didn't make it.  Oops.

This project's still alive.  Slow, but alive.
Just going over a couple of copy abilities this time and noting a little detail in their mechanics.

I would like to apologize for not replying to a lot of the questions that's gone up this past year.  Though I must say a good handful of them were answered before and/or not with the most respectful tone.
So here's a little FAQ: http://azurarokstudio.deviantart.com/journal/KCCh-Q-amp-A-2013-346509491

At any rate, I shouldn't be sounding too negative.  Hope everyone has a good year!
